            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#吃饭太快会增加高血压糖尿病风险#】专家表示，在主食的总摄入量中，除了精米白面，建议添加三分之一比例的全谷物。此外，吃饭速度快的人与细嚼慢咽的人...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E9%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E5%BF%AB%E4%BC%9A%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E9%A5%AD%E5%A4%AA%E5%BF%AB%E4%BC%9A%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃饭太快会增加高血压糖尿病风险#</span></a>】专家表示，在主食的总摄入量中，除了精米白面，建议添加三分之一比例的全谷物。此外，吃饭速度快的人与细嚼慢咽的人相比，患高血压的风险会增加45%，患糖尿病的风险增加73%👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视一套）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4767286154952770" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视一套的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/78ad4dbbly1h22cdp1qkkj20ru0foac5.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/DTKJgnN8lx07VUUrd9pS01041200kG5M0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1703078384&amp;ssig=wO9lqgegi9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/I1kyT8yPlx07VUUp52EM01041200bRKk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1703078384&amp;ssig=0WveryxVnX&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5A1MY0t2lx07VUUpi6Wk010412007aVk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1703078384&amp;ssig=zjvkTJzqMg&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4767286154952770" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
